data.description: This fantastic home is in a prime location, half a block off Story St., with a ton of recent updates! The hardwood floors have been refinished, new paint throughout the home, new carpet upstairs, updates to the bathroom and a new garage door! You can move in and start putting your own personal touches to make it a home.
